Framed Prints

Bring the rich history of Central Asia into your home with our exquisite Framed Prints featuring the iconic Statue of Amir Timur (Tamerlane) by MA from Discover Images by AWL. This magnificent artwork captures the essence of Tamerlane, the founder of the Timurid Empire and the first ruler of the Timurid dynasty, as depicted in the stunning statue located in Tashkent, Uzbekistan. Each print is meticulously framed to preserve the beauty and detail of the image, making it a stunning addition to any room. Immerse yourself in the history and culture of Central Asia with our Framed Prints.

Amir Timur, the founder of the Timurid Empire, is depicted with regal presence and strength, transporting you back in time to the ancient world. Our high-quality photographic print is a must-have for history enthusiasts and art collectors, adding a touch of cultural sophistication to any space.

Poster Prints

Bring the rich history of Central Asia into your home or office with our stunning Statue of Amir Timur (Tamerlane) poster print. This beautiful image, captured by MA from Discover Images by AWL, showcases the iconic statue of the founder of the Timurid Empire in Tashkent, Uzbekistan. Amir Timur, also known as Tamerlane, was a legendary military leader and ruler, whose empire extended from Eastern Europe to India. Add this captivating poster to your collection and let the story of Amir Timur inspire you every day.
